title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
